The paper deals with generating natural questions from images, which involves using both vision and language modalities. This suggests that the paper could belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) or Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper proposes a deep Bayesian learning framework, which falls under the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper deals with multimodal representations, which could also fall under the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CV and cs.CL, followed by cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.MM.
